and so is called...

493
00:53:03,159 --> 00:53:04,879
"...The Final Sign."

494
00:53:13,040 --> 00:53:16,159
l`m trying to reach the governor.
lt`s urgent.

495
00:53:17,360 --> 00:53:20,600
l told you it has to do
with Jimmy Zaragoza`s execution.

496
00:53:20,919 --> 00:53:22,639
Russell, it`s Abby.

497
00:53:23,360 --> 00:53:26,800
l`ve already spoken to his aide.
l need to speak to him directly.

498
00:53:28,239 --> 00:53:30,879
Yes, l`ll hold. Tell her l`ll call her back.

499
00:53:31,000 --> 00:53:34,879
l tried, but she`s not at home.
She says she must speak to you right now.

500
00:53:35,399 --> 00:53:38,040
Cover for me. Abby, are you all--

501
00:53:38,280 --> 00:53:41,719
lt`s not the baby`s birth date,
it`s from the Bible.

502
00:53:42,040 --> 00:53:44,239
He`s here because of the baby.

503
00:53:44,439 --> 00:53:45,919
Slow down.

504
00:53:46,439 --> 00:53:48,600
He thinks it`s a Bible sign!

505
00:53:48,719 --> 00:53:52,280
He told us about it,
but not the whole story. Listen:

506
00:53:52,679 --> 00:53:57,320
"The first infant born without a soul,
born dead as a soulless child must be--"

507
00:54:01,239 --> 00:54:03,959
No, it`s not! He`s a religious fanatic!

508
00:54:04,120 --> 00:54:07,080
He thinks if he can kill the baby,
he`ll end the world.

509
00:54:07,199 --> 00:54:09,439
-Listen to me.
-l`ve got the governor.

510
00:54:09,719 --> 00:54:12,199
Ask him to hold. l want you to go home.

511
00:54:17,800 --> 00:54:19,280
All right? l promise.

512
00:54:22,120 --> 00:54:23,679
Sorry, he wouldn`t wait.

513
00:54:24,080 --> 00:54:25,320
Oh, Christ!

514
00:54:32,760 --> 00:54:35,399
Keep working on this
and l`ll try him from home.

515
00:55:27,199 --> 00:55:30,399
Russell, are you here?

516
00:55:32,919 --> 00:55:36,600
-You won`t kill my baby.
-Your baby`s dying because it has no soul.

517
00:55:36,840 --> 00:55:39,320
-Don`t say that.
-The Guf is empty!

518
00:55:39,639 --> 00:55:41,840
l won`t let you kill my baby.

519
00:55:42,399 --> 00:55:44,639
Don`t you think l cry for man?

520
00:55:44,919 --> 00:55:48,280
l`ve tried to intercede, but God has judged!

521
00:55:49,600 --> 00:55:51,399
-Man`s sins are--
-Stay away!

522
00:55:55,040 --> 00:55:58,360
l can`t die again, Abby. l wish l could.

523
00:55:59,800 --> 00:56:03,239
-l`m His messenger.
-You`re crazy.

524
00:56:04,159 --> 00:56:06,399
-l was here before.
-Stay away.

525
00:56:07,679 --> 00:56:10,040
lt`s time for you to know, Abby.

526
00:56:12,040 --> 00:56:13,840
l came as the Lamb...

527
00:56:16,159 --> 00:56:18,879
...and l return as the Lion.

528
00:56:38,760 --> 00:56:40,479
Now l am His wrath.

529
00:56:50,320 --> 00:56:51,800
Strap her down!

530
00:56:52,840 --> 00:56:55,959
lt`s happening!
Why won`t you believe me?

531
00:56:57,439 --> 00:56:59,320
You have to believe me.

532
00:57:13,239 --> 00:57:14,280
Please.

533
00:57:20,800 --> 00:57:22,600
Will you die for Him?

534
00:57:31,239 --> 00:57:34,600
l don`t know what you could have done.
This can happen.

535
00:57:35,840 --> 00:57:39,719
l know the delusions seem extreme,
but she`s under enormous stress.

536
00:57:39,959 --> 00:57:42,919
There`s incredible guilt involved when....

537
00:57:44,479 --> 00:57:47,120
Well, you certainly know the history.

538
00:57:50,399 --> 00:57:52,040
What do we do now?

539
00:57:53,040 --> 00:57:57,679
This sounds pathetic, but the best
we can do is wait and see. Watch her.

540
00:58:00,879 --> 00:58:03,520
The baby`s fine. He`s hanging in there.

541
00:58:03,639 --> 00:58:07,199
lf this is just an episode,
she can go home in a couple of days.

542
00:58:07,840 --> 00:58:09,879
Will you be able to stay with her?

543
00:58:10,760 --> 00:58:14,399
-Not all the time.
-Then we should get you a nurse to help.

544
00:58:16,560 --> 00:58:20,040
And l think you should go home now
and get some serious rest.

545
00:58:25,120 --> 00:58:27,000
Of course, God will judge the world.

546
00:58:27,120 --> 00:58:30,320
-Could it be happening now?
-lt could happen any time.

547
00:58:30,959 --> 00:58:34,000
Jesus said the end would come
like a thief in the night.

548
00:58:34,120 --> 00:58:36,679
That belief is fundamental
to every religion.

549
00:58:36,760 --> 00:58:39,800
Moslem, Christian, Jew, Hindu.

550
00:58:40,800 --> 00:58:44,560
There are differences amongst them
as to how it will actually happen...

551
00:58:44,679 --> 00:58:48,199
...but we all believe in a Messiah
who delivers God`s wrath...

552
00:58:48,479 --> 00:58:49,800
...upon the world.

553
00:58:49,959 --> 00:58:54,000
Then it could be happening.
The moon has turned to blood.

554
00:58:54,199 --> 00:58:57,000
l told you about the paper and the fish.

555
00:58:57,560 --> 00:59:01,199
Yes. ln Revelation,
it is written that the sea will die.

556
00:59:01,840 --> 00:59:05,360
-Then you do see it?
-With perfect clarity.

557
00:59:06,560 --> 00:59:09,760
l see a young man
with a very large imagination.

558
00:59:10,439 --> 00:59:13,479
What you`re forgetting is that
the prophetic signs are signs.

559
00:59:13,560 --> 00:59:16,439
They`re symbols.
They`re not meant to be taken literally.

560
00:59:16,560 --> 00:59:21,360
They`re poetry written to describe
the concept of greater divine judgement...

561
00:59:21,760 --> 00:59:24,320
...not to be checked off like a laundry list.

562
00:59:25,639 --> 00:59:27,280
So the moon and the fish?

563
00:59:27,479 --> 00:59:31,520
Coincidence. You`re forgetting
the most important aspect of eschatology.

564
00:59:32,479 --> 00:59:35,719
That when the end comes,
with it comes eternal life...

565
00:59:36,679 --> 00:59:38,679
...for those of us who are saved.

566
00:59:39,399 --> 00:59:41,760
Well, who`ll be saved, Reverend?

567
00:59:42,239 --> 00:59:45,040
The Jew doesn`t think
it will be the Moslem.

568
00:59:45,239 --> 00:59:47,560
The Moslem doesn`t think
it will be the Christian.

569
00:59:47,679 --> 00:59:50,560
The Christian doesn`t think
it will be the Buddhist.

570
00:59:50,840 --> 00:59:53,639
What if nobody is saved?
What if we`re all wrong?

571
00:59:56,239 --> 00:59:59,120
My God. What if it`s just
the Hare Krishnas?

572
01:00:01,360 --> 01:00:05,120
-You`re too young to worry so much.
-That`s what my rabbi said.

573
01:00:05,280 --> 01:00:09,000
Believe me, Avi,
someday you`ll make quite a philosopher.

574
01:00:10,840 --> 01:00:12,560
lf there is a someday.

575
01:01:13,760 --> 01:01:16,000
Hello, Mr. Quinn. She`s fine.

576
01:01:18,000 --> 01:01:20,120
Could you give me that number again?

577
01:01:23,320 --> 01:01:26,199
When? Well, l have to leave.
No, it`s impossible--

578
01:01:30,000 --> 01:01:32,080
No, she`s upstairs resting.

579
01:01:32,360 --> 01:01:33,760
l`ll tell her.

580
01:02:26,120 --> 01:02:27,360
l want my baby.

581
01:02:50,840 --> 01:02:55,320
We still house noviciates here, of course.
But we do get quite a few guests, also.

582
01:02:55,800 --> 01:02:59,239
Mostly people passing through
on their way to new parishes.

583
01:03:00,040 --> 01:03:03,000
-ls that what you`re doing, Father Lucci?
-Yes, it is.

584
01:03:03,280 --> 01:03:06,479
-Then you won`t be staying very long?
-Father Morrell?

585
01:03:15,479 --> 01:03:16,959
May l help you?

586
01:03:17,800 --> 01:03:19,719
No, Father, this is Father Lucci.

587
01:03:19,919 --> 01:03:22,159
l`m sorry. l thought that....

588
01:03:23,239 --> 01:03:25,239
But the resemblance is...

589
01:03:25,840 --> 01:03:27,239
...remarkable.

590
01:03:28,280 --> 01:03:30,199
l don`t believe we`ve met.

591
01:03:30,439 --> 01:03:33,399
No, it couldn`t be. That was long ago.

592
01:03:35,840 --> 01:03:37,239
Very long ago.

593
01:03:38,000 --> 01:03:39,159
lf you`ll excuse me.

594
01:03:39,600 --> 01:03:41,479
But the resemblance...

595
01:03:43,439 --> 01:03:44,840
...it`s remarkable!

596
01:03:48,120 --> 01:03:49,159
Really?

597
01:03:49,840 --> 01:03:51,560
Good night, Father.

598
01:04:10,080 --> 01:04:11,000
Abby?

599
01:04:18,639 --> 01:04:20,520
Why is this happening?

600
01:04:21,000 --> 01:04:22,800
God`s grace is empty.

601
01:04:23,919 --> 01:04:25,919
There`s nothing l can do.

602
01:04:26,159 --> 01:04:30,040
The signs have begun.
As each passes, the end grows closer.

603
01:04:32,239 --> 01:04:34,120
Then why are you here?

604
01:04:34,360 --> 01:04:37,000
l`m its deliverer. l`m its witness.

605
01:04:41,520 --> 01:04:44,000
What if a sign didn`t happen?

606
01:04:44,639 --> 01:04:49,159
What if a sign could be stopped before
my baby comes? What would happen?

607
01:04:49,280 --> 01:04:51,159
Please, tell me.

608
01:04:52,919 --> 01:04:54,879
Then the chain would be broken.

609
01:04:57,159 --> 01:05:00,120
But it would take something
you don`t have.

610
01:05:00,239 --> 01:05:01,360
Hope.

611
01:05:12,600 --> 01:05:15,800
How can someone who cared
so little for life...

612
01:05:16,959 --> 01:05:18,679
...give life to the world?

613
01:05:18,760 --> 01:05:19,959
l do care.

614
01:05:29,080 --> 01:05:30,639
l`m going to try.

615
01:05:33,719 --> 01:05:35,280
l`m going to try.

616
01:05:36,719 --> 01:05:38,600
Any chance at all, sir?

617
01:05:39,120 --> 01:05:42,919
What can you do now that
the federal appeal has been denied?

618
01:05:45,239 --> 01:05:49,199
With less than 24 hours to go,
can you do anything to stop the execution?

619
01:06:44,520 --> 01:06:46,719
"The windows of heaven," Mrs. Quinn...

620
01:06:47,239 --> 01:06:50,840
"...the windows of heaven are open
and the earth is rent asunder.

621
01:06:52,120 --> 01:06:53,439
"lt falls...

622
01:06:54,159 --> 01:06:56,360
"...and will not rise again!"

623
01:06:59,560 --> 01:07:01,959
Please, Mrs. Quinn, it doesn`t have to be.

624
01:07:03,120 --> 01:07:04,840
How do you know my name?

625
01:07:05,000 --> 01:07:07,959
l followed the signs. They led me to you.

626
01:07:09,639 --> 01:07:10,959
Who are you?

627
01:07:11,239 --> 01:07:14,840
A priest who`s come to help you
and your baby. We don`t have much time.

628
01:07:14,959 --> 01:07:16,000
Please.

629
01:07:26,840 --> 01:07:30,239
l know what you`re going through.
l know what`s going to happen.

630
01:07:43,760 --> 01:07:45,320
Hey, Mrs. Quinn!

631
01:07:51,479 --> 01:07:54,120
l must know everything he`s told you
if l`m to help.

632
01:07:54,239 --> 01:07:57,040
He said if l can stop a sign,
the chain will be broken.

633
01:07:57,199 --> 01:07:58,199
He said that?

634
01:07:58,320 --> 01:08:01,199
Yes, and God would grant the world
a second chance.

635
01:08:01,919 --> 01:08:03,959
Did he tell you which sign to stop?

636
01:08:04,080 --> 01:08:05,959
No, l`m trying to figure it out.

637
01:08:06,040 --> 01:08:09,320
No, no. That`s impossible.
A sign can`t be stopped.

638
01:08:09,439 --> 01:08:11,719
He wouldn`t have told me
if there weren`t a way.

639
01:08:11,840 --> 01:08:15,520
That`s why l have to know the other signs.
You said you knew them.

640
01:08:18,120 --> 01:08:21,479
God has no secrets.
The signs are contained in the seven seals.

641
01:08:21,600 --> 01:08:25,120
The first four have already begun.
The Four Horsemen of the Apocalypse.

642
01:08:25,240 --> 01:08:27,319
And their signs are almost over.

643
01:08:27,640 --> 01:08:31,000
-The fifth is the death of the last martyr.
-A death could be stopped.

644
01:08:31,120 --> 01:08:32,919
But whose? Where?

645
01:08:34,799 --> 01:08:38,439
-What about the sixth?
-The sun will turn to darkness...

646
01:08:38,640 --> 01:08:42,680
...and the earth will quake
and the stars shall fall from the sky.

647
01:08:42,799 --> 01:08:45,839
"And when the Lamb opened
the seventh seal...

648
01:08:46,000 --> 01:08:48,439
"...there was silence in heaven."

649
01:08:50,000 --> 01:08:52,279
The silence of The Guf, empty.

650
01:08:52,919 --> 01:08:55,560
The stillbirth of the soulless child.

651
01:08:57,839 --> 01:08:59,839
You are the seventh seal.

652
01:09:06,439 --> 01:09:08,240
l`m not going to let my baby die.

653
01:09:09,640 --> 01:09:11,439
One of the signs has to be stopped.

654
01:09:11,520 --> 01:09:13,399
How? Do you know how?

655
01:09:17,279 --> 01:09:18,479
With hope.

656
01:09:21,240 --> 01:09:23,399
Can hope stop an earthquake?

657
01:09:24,040 --> 01:09:27,160
Can it stop a murder
halfway around the globe?

658
01:09:28,240 --> 01:09:30,600
The fourth horseman still rides.

659
01:09:31,600 --> 01:09:35,120
The angels have unleashed the winds
from the corners of the earth.

660
01:09:35,640 --> 01:09:37,799
Can you stop that with hope?

661
01:09:51,319 --> 01:09:53,120
Will you die for Him?

662
01:10:03,240 --> 01:10:04,720
Will you die for Him?

663
01:10:06,759 --> 01:10:07,720
No!

664
01:10:13,560 --> 01:10:15,680
You hit him in my dream.

665
01:10:15,839 --> 01:10:17,399
lt was no dream.

666
01:10:18,080 --> 01:10:19,560
You were there.

667
01:10:20,240 --> 01:10:23,759
You`re not here to help.
You want the world to end.

668
01:10:23,959 --> 01:10:26,759
Yes, Mrs. Quinn. For a very long time.

669
01:10:27,959 --> 01:10:29,759
You are my deliverance.

670
01:10:34,080 --> 01:10:37,759
There`s nothing you can do.
You can`t stop it.

671
01:11:21,640 --> 01:11:23,640
What kind of God are you?

672
01:11:28,399 --> 01:11:29,600
Let me in!

673
01:11:37,279 --> 01:11:39,479
You were always nosy, Harold.

674
01:11:40,720 --> 01:11:42,439
lt is you, Morrell.

675
01:11:43,120 --> 01:11:45,680
But that was 70 years ago.

676
01:11:48,720 --> 01:11:50,879
That was just yesterday to me.

677
01:11:51,000 --> 01:11:53,120
But you haven`t aged.

678
01:11:54,279 --> 01:11:56,000
You haven`t changed.

679
01:11:56,600 --> 01:11:58,240
ln the name of God, how?

680
01:11:58,680 --> 01:12:00,720
ln the name of God is how.

681
01:12:01,680 --> 01:12:05,560
l was cursed by Him for what l had done.
l struck a man.

682
01:12:06,279 --> 01:12:08,520
But, of course, He was no man.

683
01:12:09,680 --> 01:12:11,560
He was the Son of God.

684
01:12:13,359 --> 01:12:14,919
l am Cartaphilus.

685
01:12:15,240 --> 01:12:16,959
Pilate`s gatekeeper?

686
01:12:19,160 --> 01:12:20,799
The Roman soldier who was--

687
01:12:20,879 --> 01:12:23,520
Cursed to walk the earth
until the Messiah returned.

688
01:12:23,640 --> 01:12:27,839
Cursed to live and never die,
until it was time for the world to die.

689
01:12:28,640 --> 01:12:31,200
And so it has been for 2,000 years.

690
01:12:31,439 --> 01:12:34,839
For me, there`s been no escape
from the misery of life.

691
01:12:35,040 --> 01:12:38,319
But l always knew my sentence
would not be eternal.

692
01:12:38,959 --> 01:12:40,600
And so, l win!

693
01:12:41,319 --> 01:12:44,120
An end has come! My death is at hand.

694
01:12:45,680 --> 01:12:48,879
l won`t be stopped by anyone.
Not her, not you.

695
01:12:50,560 --> 01:12:52,120
l can`t allow it.

696
01:12:53,080 --> 01:12:56,040
You understand, don`t you, old friend?

697
01:13:07,040 --> 01:13:08,359
Thank you.

698
01:13:14,359 --> 01:13:15,919
Did you see him?

699
01:13:22,160 --> 01:13:23,560
l`m gonna die?

700
01:13:27,160 --> 01:13:30,240
l tried, Jimmy. l did everything l could.

701
01:13:34,240 --> 01:13:36,120
They don`t understand.

702
01:13:37,160 --> 01:13:39,720
Do you think God will forgive them?

703
01:13:46,720 --> 01:13:48,120
l don`t know.

704
01:13:55,919 --> 01:13:58,560
So we`ve got to stop this death.
Whose death?

705
01:13:58,680 --> 01:14:01,640
l don`t know.
lt`s somebody who`s a martyr.

706
01:14:01,839 --> 01:14:05,080
-That`s the fourth sign?
-No, l think it`s the fifth.

707
01:14:06,080 --> 01:14:08,799
The last martyr, an earthquake and....

708
01:14:09,000 --> 01:14:12,879
l don`t know. l can`t think anymore.
You should know this!

709
01:14:13,240 --> 01:14:15,959
That`s not my book,
it`s the New Testament.

710
01:14:16,279 --> 01:14:18,439
Pull over. Pull over there!

711
01:14:28,919 --> 01:14:31,720
-What are you doing?
-Getting us a Bible!

712
01:14:44,319 --> 01:14:45,799
We need a room!

713
01:14:51,319 --> 01:14:52,359
Thirty bucks.

714
01:14:59,399 --> 01:15:03,359
-Got it. Revelation 5. "A Scroll--"
-Read me the sixth sign.

715
01:15:06,439 --> 01:15:10,040
"When he broke the sixth seal,
there was a great earthquake...

716
01:15:10,160 --> 01:15:14,200
"...and the sun became black as sackcloth
and the moon became red as blood."

717
01:15:16,000 --> 01:15:18,720
An eclipse.
lt`s on my calendar for tomorrow.

718
01:15:19,040 --> 01:15:21,080
Go back to the fifth sign.

719
01:15:22,759 --> 01:15:27,200
"When He opened the fifth seal, l saw the
souls of those slain for the word of God.

720
01:15:27,359 --> 01:15:32,000
"They cried, `Lord, when wilt thou avenge
our blood on those on the earth?`

721
01:15:32,319 --> 01:15:35,959
"They were told to rest until the number
of their brethren was complete...

722
01:15:36,080 --> 01:15:38,720
"...who were to be killed
as they themselves had been."

723
01:15:38,839 --> 01:15:40,640
The death of the last martyr.

724
01:15:40,759 --> 01:15:44,160
lt`s someone who dies for the word of God,
before the eclipse.

725
01:15:45,040 --> 01:15:45,919
How?

726
01:15:47,479 --> 01:15:49,680
Tortured to death? Murdered?

727
01:15:56,399 --> 01:15:57,520
Executed.

728
01:16:03,160 --> 01:16:07,359
Attorneys were unable to get
a stay of execution for Jimmy Zaragoza...

729
01:16:07,600 --> 01:16:11,160
...the "Word of God Killer,"
whose parents were brother and sister.

730
01:16:11,279 --> 01:16:14,560
He murdered them, he said,
"because it was God`s law. "

731
01:16:14,680 --> 01:16:18,120
This morning, Jimmy will die
according to man`s law.

732
01:17:01,399 --> 01:17:02,959
Hello?

733
01:17:04,560 --> 01:17:06,839
Abby, where are you?

734
01:17:06,959 --> 01:17:09,080
Russell, l know how to stop it.

735
01:17:11,600 --> 01:17:12,640
An eclipse?

736
01:17:14,680 --> 01:17:16,680
Abby, l can`t stop the execution.

737
01:17:16,839 --> 01:17:20,040
You must. He is the last martyr.
You can`t let them kill him.

738
01:17:20,720 --> 01:17:23,439
There`s nothing l can do.
Tell me where you are.

739
01:17:24,240 --> 01:17:26,160
Abby, are you all right?

740
01:17:27,080 --> 01:17:29,200
l`ll meet you at the prison.

741
01:17:29,359 --> 01:17:31,000
No! You can`t stop--

742
01:17:31,200 --> 01:17:32,759
l`m going to leave now.

743
01:19:54,919 --> 01:19:59,200
Penny! Thank God! You`ve got to
get me in! You`ve got to help me.

744
01:20:39,520 --> 01:20:41,879
Okay, breathe, breathe.

745
01:21:37,720 --> 01:21:38,680
Stop!

746
01:21:48,959 --> 01:21:50,359
Somebody stop him!

747
01:22:33,839 --> 01:22:35,640
l did it. lt`s over.

748
01:22:37,759 --> 01:22:39,080
Somebody....

749
01:22:41,919 --> 01:22:43,479
Somebody help us!

750
01:22:45,720 --> 01:22:46,799
No!

751
01:22:50,720 --> 01:22:52,279
Somebody help us!

752
01:22:52,919 --> 01:22:54,399
lt`s all right, Abby.

753
01:22:55,359 --> 01:22:56,759
God, no!

754
01:24:05,720 --> 01:24:08,040
Sorry. lt`s all my fault.

755
01:24:08,799 --> 01:24:10,359
lt`s all right, Abby.

756
01:24:17,120 --> 01:24:18,600
Breathe deeply.

757
01:24:21,879 --> 01:24:23,200
Relax. Breathe.

758
01:24:40,600 --> 01:24:42,000
All right, push.

759
01:24:45,919 --> 01:24:47,399
-Breathe, Abby.
-Push!

760
01:24:51,160 --> 01:24:52,560
You`re fine.

761
01:25:02,799 --> 01:25:07,000
lt`s all right. You`re doing good.
Deep breaths!

762
01:25:09,600 --> 01:25:11,160
Can you do it one more time?

763
01:25:11,240 --> 01:25:12,959
One more time, Abby.

764
01:25:18,479 --> 01:25:20,479
That a girl. Come on, push!

765
01:25:25,080 --> 01:25:27,560
Hold on! The head is out!

766
01:25:28,720 --> 01:25:31,120
Come on, sweetheart, we`re almost there!

767
01:25:38,759 --> 01:25:40,720
We`ve lost the baby`s heartbeat.

768
01:25:48,879 --> 01:25:50,680
Will you die for Him?

769
01:25:52,560 --> 01:25:54,120
Will you die for Him?

770
01:25:55,799 --> 01:25:57,359
Yes, l will!

771
01:25:59,200 --> 01:26:01,399
l will die for Him.

772
01:26:05,040 --> 01:26:07,160
l will die for Him.

773
01:28:19,919 --> 01:28:21,799
He`s beautiful, Abby...

774
01:28:24,680 --> 01:28:26,919
...just like you said he`d be.

775
01:28:29,200 --> 01:28:30,919
You can`t see him...

776
01:28:32,319 --> 01:28:33,879
...but you know.

777
01:28:36,200 --> 01:28:37,759
You always knew.

778
01:28:55,399 --> 01:28:57,759
The Hall of Souls is full again.

779
01:29:02,439 --> 01:29:03,759
lt was you, Abby.

780
01:29:06,040 --> 01:29:09,759
Just the one person with hope enough
for the whole world.

781
01:29:34,479 --> 01:29:36,040
Remember it all.

782
01:29:37,080 --> 01:29:38,479
Write it down.

783
01:29:39,879 --> 01:29:41,080
Tell it...

784
01:29:42,600 --> 01:29:46,040
...so people will use the chance
she has given them.

